snippet.title: hellrider 3 - early beta trailer (2019)
snippet.description:
A new part of the mobile arcade about brave racers and insidious skeletons! The following video shows a work in progress. The game is developed by one person in the course of 16 months. 
Visit - https://twitter.com/AnjiGames
My other games - https://cargocollective.com/AnjiGames
